  <brief_title>Geko Venous Leg Ulcer Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single Centre Open Label Pilot Study Measuring Lower Limb Blood Flow in Patients With Venous Leg Ulcers Using the Geko™ T-2 or gekoTM Plus [R-2] Neuromuscular Electro Stimulation Device</official_title>
